# Implementation Plan - Redesign: Dark + Gray + Blue (v4.0)

Complete overhaul of the website aesthetic to a "Dark Tech" theme with deep blues and slate grays, emphasizing precision and industrial authority.

## Design Specification

- **Base Background**: `#0a0b10` (Deep Onyx)
- **Primary Accent**: `#3a86ff` (Electric Blue)
- **Gray Tiers**: `#1c1e26` (Slate), `#2d313d` (Charcoal)
- **Typography**: `Inter` for body, `Outfit` or `Montserrat` for bold headlines.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Global Design System

#### [MODIFY] [global.css](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/jin-hong-me-html-v2/css/global.css)

- Reset CSS variables to the new "Dark + Gray + Blue" palette.
- Implement glassmorphism utility classes (`.glass-card`).
- Add asymmetrical grid layouts (`.asym-grid`).
- Update all button variants to follow the new neon/glow style.

### 2. Homepage Overhaul

#### [MODIFY] [index.html](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/antigravity/jin-hong-me-html-v2/index.html)

